      <title>CoreWeave 表示，数据中心的人工智能需求被大大低估</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ai-demand-for-data-centers-vastly-underestimated-coreweave-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[云计算独角兽 CoreWeave 的联合创始人表示，世界“严重”低估了人工智能的需求将在未来五年内扩大全球数据中心市场的规模。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ai-demand-for-data-centers-vastly-underestimated-coreweave-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 20:28:25 GMT</pubDate>
